                    </p>
                </Card>
            </div>

            <div class='col-span-4 p-4 m-4 custom-lavender-texture-bg border-dashed border-b-dark drop-shadow-[5px_5px_0_rgb(0_0_0/_1)]'>
                <Card>
                    <h2 class='text-2xl md:text-4xl outfit font-bold mb-4 rubik-variable'>Why Follow Along?</h2>
